QuestData.Title: Meet Me Up Top
QuestData.Description: I never thought that I would be a prisoner of the Alliance again. I cannot begin to express my gratitude to you... $n, is it?$B$BI will meet you up top and from there we will deal with them.
QuestData.LogDescription: Make your way up top on the upper deck of the Vengeance Wake off the shore of the Lost Isles and speak with Thrall.
QuestData.RewardText: My mission is too critical to let these meddlers continue to dog us. It's up to you and I to put an end to this once and for all!
